text: Jürgen Prutsch (born September 22, 1989 in Graz) is an Austrian professional football player. Currently, he plays for Italian Lega Pro Prima Divisione side Barletta on loan from A.S. Livorno Calcio. He made his Serie A debut for A.S. Livorno Calcio on March 24, 2010 in a game against F.C.
